{"id":"812599051589648384","type":"text","timestamp":1774954845,"post_url":"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/goodtransgirl/812599051589648384","is_reblog":true,"added_content":true,"tags":[],"reblog_ready":true,"body":"<p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/goodtransgirl/811421372089794560\">goodtransgirl</a>:</p><blockquote><p>So, I&rsquo;ve seen this post from @tpwrtrmnky around and I&rsquo;m pretty sure I reblogged it along the way.  </p><div class=\"npf_row\"><figure class=\"tmblr-full\" data-orig-height=\"209\" data-orig-width=\"552\"><img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/bf422842861e65f3ff379e375871e58e/732a9aaf69232b24-77/s640x960/b675e16ebcfb6aa9660b8add3497c1a9b35c73e9.png\" data-orig-height=\"209\" data-orig-width=\"552\" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/bf422842861e65f3ff379e375871e58e/732a9aaf69232b24-77/s75x75_c1/964b6a2d48d8e4a6d57a99ea661147f2dd2d1be9.png 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/bf422842861e65f3ff379e375871e58e/732a9aaf69232b24-77/s100x200/9ed95460eafc6d31491cd38d88166b81acd733bd.png 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/bf422842861e65f3ff379e375871e58e/732a9aaf69232b24-77/s250x400/5618593b8782bfc90441c835acdb812d4178cd98.png 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/bf422842861e65f3ff379e375871e58e/732a9aaf69232b24-77/s400x600/711a25488e3cc9dd915efad92e380bb7bc361904.png 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/bf422842861e65f3ff379e375871e58e/732a9aaf69232b24-77/s500x750/4e5c84dfc038f3ad8cfe7a8d7ce7ea34a53a3c65.png 500w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/bf422842861e65f3ff379e375871e58e/732a9aaf69232b24-77/s540x810/4396e13db067203d4cc8ae7e90e3d5f63b2ac238.png 540w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/bf422842861e65f3ff379e375871e58e/732a9aaf69232b24-77/s640x960/b675e16ebcfb6aa9660b8add3497c1a9b35c73e9.png 552w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 552px) 100vw, 552px\"/></figure></div><p>And it&rsquo;s been bebopping around in my head ever since.  I joke at times that I &ldquo;transitioned too late.&rdquo;  And I do wish I&rsquo;d done it sooner, but I th